quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf. Nditsuba khukurani yoluyali."
  50,2,"Bawukanga mbu Omwikanyilisi yabeetsela okhurula mubo! Abakhayi nibaboola mbu: “Po, kano nikokhuchenyia."
  50,3,"Mbu nikhulifwa mana khube liloba, okhukalukha okho khuli ehale (shikhunyalikhana tawe).”"
  50,4,"Toto khwamanya shiosishiosi shilemukha khusialo mubo, ne khuli nende eshitabo eshibikhanga koosi."
  50,5,"Halali bakhaya obwatoto olwabwabeetsela, mana abo bali mubukoyanu."
  50,6,"Shibalolangakhwo likulu hekulu wabu, shingala khwaliumbakha mana nikhulirona, shililikhwo nolwafwa tawe?"
  50,7,"Ne liloba khwalikwaalasia mana nikhuliramwo tsingulu, mana nikhumesiakhwo buli imbia yemimela emilayi."
  50,8,"Kho shibe eshilolelo nende eshitsulisio khu buli omusumba ukalukha khu Nyasaye."
  50,9,"Ne khweshia amaatsi ketsikhabi okhurula mwikulu, nikhukamesilia emikunda nende imele ichesungwa."
  50,10,"Nende emitende emirambi chilikhwo ebibuli (chiebulana mubunji)."
  50,11,"Omukabo khubasumba banje, mana nikhulamusia khuko eshialo shiali nishifwile, ne ni endio nilwa Abandu balilamusibwa."
  50,12,"Bakhaya imbeli wabu Abandu ba Nuhu, nende Abandu ba Rasi nende ba Thamud."
  50,13,"Nende ba Aa’d, nende ba Firauni nende Abana babu Luti."
  50,14,"Nende abamenyi ba Aikat (bomumasokholio), nende Abandu ba Tubaa, boosi bakhaya Abarumwa mana kabekanyilisibwa nikabanyoola."
  50,15,"Ne muparanga khwachong’a olwa khwabaloonga olwo khuranga? Halali bo bali nobukoyani khukhuloongwa okhuyiakha."
  50,16,"Ne toto khwaloonga Omundu, ne khwamanya shimubeyibeyinjia mumwoyo kukwe, nafu khuli ahambi muno khuye okhushila omusi kwo mwikosi we."
  50,17,"Olwa Abamalaika babili balibukana, owundi niyekhala omukhono omulunji ne owundi omukaata."
  50,18,"Shiyakhaboola liosiliosi tawe halali hali nende omulenji werechekha obulayi muno (owuhandikanga)."
  50,19,"Ne tsisaalila tsiokhurula omwoyo tsiliitsa khubwatoto. Ako niko kawerukhanga."
  50,20,"Ne olwika lulifurwamwo, eyo niyo inyaanga yokhunyola amabii kalakwa."
  50,21,"Ne buli Omundu aliitsa nali nende Omuliindi nende Omuloli."
  50,22,"Aboolelwe mbu: “Toto ewe wali wang’ang’ala ehale nende kano, mana khukhuyiniyekhwo shiakhwikalilanga okhulola, kho okhulola khukhwo nyanga yino nokhulayi muno.”"
  50,23,"Ne owashie aliboola mbu: “Wendi ninaye uno amalile okhurechekhwa.”"
  50,24,"(Nyasaye aboole): “Sukune mumulilo buli omukhayi po, omwandakanyu."
  50,25,"Owikalilanga amalayi, wabura eshichelo, owobukanakani."
  50,26,"Ulia watsokaasia Nyasaye nende abanyasaye baandi, kho mumusukune mushinyasio eshilulu.”"
  50,27,"Owashe aliboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, esie shindamukosia tawe halali ye yali mubukori obwa ehale.”"
  50,28,"Nyasaye aliboola mbu: “Mulasolana imbeli wanje tawe, ndamala okhubarumila amekanyilisio."
  50,29,"Liumaho likalukhanibungwa imbeli wanje tawe, ne esie shekholelanga Abasumba banje obubii tawe.”"
  50,30,"Inyanga yakhulireba (omuliro kwa) Jahannam mbu: “Witsuule?” Nayo ilikalusia mbu: “Abaandi baliwo umete?”"
  50,31,"Ne omukunda kwomwikulu (Janna) kulisitibwa hambi khu baria Nyasaye."
  50,32,"Kano niko kamulakungwa khu ulia ukalukha muno khu Nyasaye mana niyelinda po."
  50,33,"Ulia waria Nyasaye khukefisile, mana niyetsa nende omwoyo omulunjifu."
  50,34,"""Injilemwo nomulembe, ino ni inyanga yokhumenya obulaliwa tawe.”"
  50,35,"Balinyoolamwo shiosishiosi shiabeenya, ne khuli nende ebindi ebinji."
  50,36,"Ne ni tsingongo tsinga tsiakhwasishia imbeli wabu, bali nende amaani okhushila bano! Mana nibayiya khushialo muno, koo banyolakhwo wabelushila?"
  50,37,"Toto mu ako, shilimwo eshitsulisio khu ulia uli nomwoyo nohomba owareka eshirwi naye naaliho obulai (nalolanga)."
  50,38,"Ne toto khwaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende bioosi bilimwo khutsinyanga tsisasaba, ne shikhwanyoola obuchonyi bwosibwosi tawe."
  50,39,"Kho, wisumilisie khukababoolanga, ne mutswenule Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khutsifumia tsitsie tsindayi eliuba nilishili okhurula nende nilishili okhukwa."
  50,40,"Ne mutswenule khandi eshilo nende niwakhamala okhumurerera obweni hasi (okhusujuda)."
  50,41,"Ne rechelesia inyanga yomulaanji alilanga okhurulila habundu ahambi."
  50,42,"Inyanga yabaliwulila oluyoka lwomulango kwa toto. Eyo niyo inyanga yokhurula (mubilindwa)."
  50,43,"Toto efwe nefwe balamusinjia khandi bafwisinjia, ne ewefu niwa amakalushilo."
  50,44,"Inyanga yeshialo shiliatikha barula lwangu lwangu. Okhukhung’asibwa okho khuliba okhwangu khwifwe."
  50,45,"Efwe khumanyile muno kababoolanga, ne ewe shobarukanga na amaani tawe. Kho wikhoonyele Ikuran okhwitsulisia balia abaria ambii akalakwa (okhurulila inyanga yeyindukho)."
